originalText.text: Laurie is truly amazing! I've been seeing Laurie for almost two years now and I have to say, of all the different therapists I've seen over the past 20 years Laurie is, by far, the best therapist I have ever had.  She does all the things that are expected of good therapists (like active listening, validation, and empathy), but she also offers you alterative perspectives that are arguably healthier, rooted in reason, and often eye-opening. She challenges you to step outside your comfort zone but does not judge you when you hesitate or struggle. I hope I never move out of the area because Laurie has set the bar so high, it'll be difficult for me to be satisfied with anyone else!
